WEBVTT

00:00.900 --> 00:04.980
You see, in Sahaja Yoga, you are not given
any mantra or anything.

00:04.980 --> 00:09.660
There’s no, nothing like giving you into
a big course, like teaching you one after

00:09.660 --> 00:12.870
another any mantra, or anything, it’s not
like that.

00:12.870 --> 00:18.210
What you have to know: where the Kundalini
is, how it is moving, where it is, what is

00:18.210 --> 00:21.099
the charka catching and what is the mantra
for that.

00:21.099 --> 00:25.300
It doesn’t take anything, hardly it takes
about a week for you to understand the all

00:25.300 --> 00:26.300
thing.

00:26.300 --> 00:29.840
But gradually, as you start using it, you
become proficient and you how to do it for

00:29.840 --> 00:31.499
yourself and for others.

00:31.499 --> 00:38.840
There is not much of a thing- like a child,
when he comes up a little age, he starts speaking

00:38.840 --> 00:43.140
up language, because he has a built-in capacity
to create sounds.

00:43.140 --> 00:45.390
And he does it.

00:45.390 --> 00:50.610
In the same way, once you get it, when you
get the cool breeze in you hand, you learn

00:50.610 --> 00:57.330
it by using it, you understand it yourself,
you become yourself quite proficient.

00:57.330 --> 01:00.750
And you will be amazed how fast you learn
this.

01:00.750 --> 01:05.800
You don’t have to learn it just like a science
book or anything, you just start learning,

01:05.800 --> 01:09.590
you can: this is charka which is catching
because now, say, for example, this charka

01:09.590 --> 01:11.100
is catching [fore finger], right side.

01:11.100 --> 01:13.870
Now, there’s a mantra for this is of Shri
Krishna.

01:13.870 --> 01:20.740
Say, this charka is catching [forehead], here,
then there’s a mantra of Jesus Christ.

01:20.740 --> 01:24.200
Like that, you must know the mantras and the
charkas.

01:24.200 --> 01:30.270
But the charkas you just know as a, absolutely,
a knowledge which is built-in your nerves:

01:30.270 --> 01:33.130
you just feel it.

01:33.130 --> 01:35.880
This is- now this gentleman is saying: ” it’s
hot here” [left palm].

01:35.880 --> 01:36.880
