01:43.110 --> 01:45.060
Now, on the left side it’s there.

01:45.060 --> 01:48.450
So that means there’s a mantra for that,
and that one must be used.

01:48.450 --> 01:52.049
If you use that mantra, this will be cleared
out.

01:52.049 --> 01:53.049
Alright?

01:53.049 --> 01:54.560
That is how you have to know.

01:54.560 --> 01:59.970
And that’s why I said it takes time for
people sometimes to establish, because first

01:59.970 --> 02:02.110
you have to know it and then use it.

